<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Favourer" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Favourer,</orth> one who favours and assists, a friend: <cit><quote>as --s, not as foes,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 1.4.73" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 4, 73</bibl></cit>. With <cit><quote>of:</quote> <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.80" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 80</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 9</bibl>. With <cit><quote>to:</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.3.74" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 3, 74</bibl></cit>.
